    <p>THE CHRIST­MAS CHRON­I­CLES: PART TWO (PG) 115 min­utes/Net­flix</p>
    <p>When a rogue elf threat­ens to de­stroy the North Pole and end Christ­mas, Santa Claus and his wife (Kurt Rus­sell and Goldie Hawn, both above) get help from teenagers Kate (Darby Camp) and Jack (Jahzir Bruno).</p>
    <p>This Net­flix ad­ven­ture-com­edy for the whole fam­ily is set two years af­ter the orig­i­nal. It is di­rected and pro­duced by Chris Colum­bus, the man be­hind Christ­mas clas­sics Home Alone (1990) and Home Alone 2: Lost In New York (1992), as well as Harry Pot­ter And The Sor­cerer’s Stone (2001) and Harry Pot­ter And The Cham­ber Of Se­crets (2002).</p>

